##  What's changed
- Fix anoying bug in chart tooltip.
- Added z-settings to markArea functionality to control if your areas are behind or in front of the Chart.

## What's Changed

* Dynamically change column number in Trade detail based on pane size not screen size by @Mohammad699 in https://github.com/freqtrade/frequi/pull/2536

## New Contributors
* @Mohammad699 made their first contribution in https://github.com/freqtrade/frequi/pull/2536

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/freqtrade/frequi/compare/2.0.6...2.0.7

## What's Changed

- Display Enter / exit tags on signals independent of executions (can be disabled via plot-config)
- Allow configuration of initially displayed number candle for charts.
